videos.description: Kyric McGowan finds the open gap and rushes for a 79-yard Northwestern touchdown, the Wildcats' first TD since October 5.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (McGowan goes the distance for a 79-yard TD) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: McGowan goes the distance for a 79-yard TD

videos.description: Aiden Smith throws up the middle to Jase James, who plunges into the end zone for a 16-yard Northwestern touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (James reels in the diving TD catch) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: James reels in the diving TD catch

videos.description: Purdue freshman King Doerue runs the ball to the outside for a 12-yard score, his team-high seventh touchdown of the season.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Doerue gets his 7th TD of the season) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Doerue gets his 7th TD of the season

videos.description: Amad Anderson hangs on for a high 11-yard touchdown catch that almost slips through his fingers, giving Purdue an early second half lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Anderson scores by this fingertips) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Anderson scores by this fingertips

videos.description: Aiden Smith launches the 8-yard touchdown pass to Riley Lees, taking back the lead for the Wildcats early in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Lees gets both feet down for the leading TD) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lees gets both feet down for the leading TD

videos.description: J.D. Dellinger sends a 39-yard kick straight through the uprights with three seconds left to give Purdue a 24-22 win over Northwestern.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Dellinger's game-winning kick lifts Purdue) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dellinger's game-winning kick lifts Purdue
